|               |   Sort: to_timestamp(hits.EventTime) ASC NULLS LAST, hits.SearchPhrase ASC NULLS LAST, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
